## Versioning Strategy

All APIs are versioned via URL path prefix: `/api/v1/`

## Response Envelope

```json
{
  "data": {},
  "error": null,
  "meta": {
    "request_id": "string",
    "timestamp": "ISO8601"
  }
}
```

## Error Format

```json
{
  "data": null,
  "error": {
    "code": "ERROR_CODE",
    "message": "Human-readable description",
    "details": {}
  }
}
```

## Standard Status Codes

| Code | Meaning |
|------|---------|
| 200 | Success |
| 201 | Created |
| 400 | Bad Request (validation error) |
| 401 | Unauthenticated |
| 403 | Forbidden |
| 404 | Not Found |
| 409 | Conflict |
| 422 | Unprocessable Entity |
| 500 | Internal Server Error |

